      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://deps.cloud/docs/deploy/config/indexing/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;This section provides guidance on how to configure the underlying system.
Keep in mind, how you update the configuration depends on your deployment strategy.
If you&amp;rsquo;re using Docker, you will be changing the &lt;code&gt;config.yaml&lt;/code&gt; file.
If you&amp;rsquo;re using Kubernetes, you will need to change the &lt;code&gt;config.yaml&lt;/code&gt; key in the &lt;code&gt;depscloud-indexer&lt;/code&gt; &lt;code&gt;Secret&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
